\v 25 And they captured two of the officers of Midian, Oreb and Zeeb, and they killed Oreb at the rock of Oreb and they killed Zeeb at the wine press of Zeeb and they pursued\f + \ft them\f* to Midian and they brought the heads of Oreb and Zeeb to Gideon from across the Jordan.